! a group before we can expect a better than even chance that at least 2
! independent people in a group share a common birthday. Furthermore:
! Simulate and thus estimate when we can expect a better than even chance
! that at least 3, 4 & 5 independent people of the group share a common
! birthday. For simplicity assume that all of the people are alive...
